node.text:
This Pride, I’m supporting @unileverusa’s #UnitedWeStand - a campaign to platform underrepresented LGBTQ+ narratives across the US and champion frontline and systematic change at grassroots and local levels. 

Across the year, Unilever will be supporting the work of @freedomoklahoma, @forumforequality, @tko_alabama, @PFLAGsgf, @scblackPride. 

In this film by @tourmaliiine, meet Darius & Gertie from South Carolina, two remarkable people continuing the legacy of Marsha P Johnson’s vision to unite the Black LGBTQ+ community. 

Alongside the film, @UnileverUSA is supporting @scblackPride to enhance their work addressing food insecurity amongst the Black LGBTQ+ community and decriminalizing HIV, where they are joining statewide stakeholders to begin writing policy that would change the current laws as it pertains to HIV in the state. 

Visit www.southcarolinablackpride.com to find out how to support

Watch the full series of films at @tourmaliiine

#UnileverPartner #Pride2021
